title: MAIDS Notification 2025 - Apply Offline for Project Scientist II Posts
description: The Maulana Azad Institute of Dental Sciences (MAIDS) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 01 Project Scientist II Posts. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their MDS can apply for the MAIDS Notification 2025. The interested applicants can apply in offline mode. Here we have mentioned the education details, age limit, selection process, application...
